---
import UptimeStatus from "../ui/UptimeStatus.astro";
import PlayerCount from "../ui/PlayerCount.astro";
import ServerAge from "../ui/ServerAge.astro";
---

<section id="nosotros" class="py-24 px-4 relative z-10 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative">
    <!-- Decorative Glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#55ffff]/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
        data-i18n="about.title"
      >
        Sobre <span
          class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#55ffff] to-[#00cccc]"
          >Nosotros</span
        >
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div
      class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl animate-fade-in-up delay-100 relative overflow-hidden group"
    >
      <!-- Subtle shine effect -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-white/5 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 pointer-events-none"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.p1">
            Desde 2020, QuickLand ha sido el hogar de miles de jugadores hispanohablantes.
            Un equipo apasionado que entiende lo que realmente importa: diversión, equidad y comunidad.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed" data-i18n="about.p2">
            Con más de 4 años de experiencia, ofrecemos un servidor estable, seguro y
            constantemente actualizado. Tu aventura de Minecraft merece lo mejor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 relative z-10">
          <!-- Row 1 - Uptime (full width) -->
          <UptimeStatus />
          <!-- Row 2 - Players and Years in same row -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <PlayerCount />
            <ServerAge />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
